@page "/vision"

<h3 class="text-center mb-4">Our Vision</h3>

<div class="container">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="images/haven.jpg" alt="Vision Image 1" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <p>At F&A Restaurant, our vision is to create a culinary haven where creativity meets quality. We strive to be a trendsetter in the culinary world, offering innovative dishes that delight the senses.</p>

            <p>We envision a dining experience that goes beyond the ordinary, where each dish is a masterpiece crafted with precision and passion. Our commitment to excellence is reflected in every aspect of our service, from the menu selection to the ambiance.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-2">
            <img src="images/community.jpg" alt="Vision Image 2" class="img-fluid rounded mb-4" />
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6 order-md-1">
            <p>Our vision extends to creating a community of food enthusiasts who appreciate the artistry behind each dish. We aim to be a culinary destination where individuals come together to celebrate flavors, culture, and creativity.</p>

            <p>Join us on this journey as we envision a future filled with culinary exploration, memorable dining experiences, and a shared passion for exceptional food.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

